            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1644840751668-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1644840751668-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>cooled rice</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and<strong> </strong>the <strong>remaining toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until everything is combined and the rice is heated through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1644840781057-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1644840781057-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1644840781057-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1644840781057-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1644840781057-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once combined, push the rice to one side of the pot and crack your <strong>egg[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>into the other side</p><p>Stir the <strong>egg</strong> with a wooden spoon to break the yolk<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and cook for 1-2 min or until resembling scrambled egg</p><p>Once resembling scrambled egg, mix it all through the rice along with the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong> – this is your <strong>egg fried rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1644840846970-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1644840846970-x400.jpg",
